# FlowBoard Implementation Plan

> **For agentic workers:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:subagent-driven-development (recommended) or superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task. Steps use checkbox (`- [ ]`) syntax for tracking.

**Goal:** Build a full Trello-like Kanban board app (FlowBoard) with drag-and-drop, modals, dark mode, and multi-board navigation.

**Architecture:** Next.js 14 App Router with a single-page layout (sidebar + header + board). Zustand stores all state in a flat card map with column ID arrays; @hello-pangea/dnd handles drag-and-drop; Framer Motion handles modal/card animations.

**Tech Stack:** Next.js 14, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS v3, Zustand, @hello-pangea/dnd, Framer Motion, Lucide React

